description: this is a compilation of webcam photos from anacam, the internet's 1st webcam to be art. this was a performance art piece for The Sex Worker's Art show.  the song is by me, Ana Voog. called "breathe you out" from my album Spool Forka Dish on Columbia records. i wrote the song and played all the instruments except the drums by Bobby Z of Prince and the Revolution.
